headline: CoreWeave and Dell Technologies Extend Relationship to Deliver AI at Scale
summary: Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL) is expanding its strategic relationship with AI hyperscaler, CoreWeave, as the first to ship Dell PowerEdge XE9712 server racks with NVIDIA GB200 NVL72 to support CoreWeave's Cloud Services Platform. CoreWeave will receive1 liquid-cooled, fully-integrated Dell IR7000 racks with Dell PowerEdge XE9712 servers, supported by Dell's AI professional services to optimize CoreWeave's data center design.
